      • saveConfig

        private void saveConfig()
        Responsible for pushing some of the config date for the plugin manager into the main user config. Note that this doesn't actually persist the data, that is only done on a clean exit of the GUI by code hidden somewhere else.

      • downloadFile

        private void downloadFile(String name,
                URL url,
                File file)
                   throws IOException
        Download a file from a URL into a local file while updating the progress panel so the user knows how far through we are
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the plugin for the progress feedback
        url - the URL to download from
        file - the file to save into
        Throws:
        IOException - if any IO related problems occur
